flowchart TD
  A[Agent (Claude Code / Cursor / OpenHands)] -->|LLM API calls via base_url| P[Context Gateway Proxy]

  P --> M{Monitor
  token usage}
  M -->|below threshold| FWD[Forward request to LLM provider]
  FWD --> L[LLM Provider (OpenAI/Anthropic/Ollama/Bedrock)]
  L --> P
  P --> A

  M -->|tool output detected| C[Intent-conditioned
  tool-output compression]
  C --> S[Store original output
  (for expand())]
  C --> FWD

  M -->|>= threshold (e.g., 75-85%)| B[Background history
  compaction job]
  B --> R[Replace long history
  with compressed history]
  R --> FWD

  A -.->|later needs removed detail| E[expand()]
  E --> P
  P --> S
  S --> P
  P --> A
